evolve from there. But again, like the landscape now versus then is like, it's foreign today.

00:24:31.060 --> 00:24:34.180
It really is. It's a, it's a totally different, it's a totally different world.

00:24:35.219 --> 00:24:38.900
So I think our advice, if you're like entering data science today,

00:24:38.900 --> 00:24:43.060
the best piece of advice we can give you is like be born 10 years earlier.

00:24:44.979 --> 00:24:46.180
Time, time travel.

00:24:46.180 --> 00:24:47.140
Just, just do that.

00:24:47.780 --> 00:24:53.619
I think there's like, I think what we've seen, or at least what I've seen is there's,

