cautious and very intentional about the pursuit of that. But I also think that there's a lot of,

00:25:02.900 --> 00:25:08.500
there's, there's continual value in sort of your own hands-on experience. People talk a lot about

00:25:08.500 --> 00:25:14.339
like the value of a portfolio, which you could debate, like how good is it to have an impressive

